title: Foundry docker image couldn't be built
body:
### Component

Forge, Cast, Anvil

### Have you ensured that all of these are up to date?

- [ ] Foundry
- [ ] Foundryup

### What version of Foundry are you on?

master, nightly

### What command(s) is the bug in?

docker build

### Operating System

macOS (Apple Silicon)

### Describe the bug

Docker image couldn't be built 

Tried to build foundry docker image and use cast in it, but wasn't able to do it.

Docker build command: 

```bash
docker build -t foundry .
```
